Gond is a deity worshiped in Faerun and Zakhara. His portfolio includes artifice, blacksmiths, construction, craft, and smithwork. He is neutral in Alignment.
His Realm in the Outlands is called Wonderhome. Wonderhome is a great workshop filled with inventions, some known in Faerun and some as yet undiscovered. 

